data.description: All of the comforts of home! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home features custom stained cabinetry and stainless steel appliances in the kitchen. The open floor plan is complemented by a gas fireplace with a mantle, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Recent upgrades include new carpet and fresh paint throughout the house. The property also boasts a convenient 2-car garage with shelving. The fenced outdoor oasis boasts a heated in-ground saltwater pool providing a relaxing oasis. Additionally, the house is equipped with an air purification system and a RING security system for added comfort and safety. Lastly, a Sunsetter powered awning enhances the outdoor space, offering shade and comfort on sunny days.
